# `live_spq_certidao.html` is a **captured wire artifact** — a real `consultaCertidao.aspx`
# response with every identifying value substituted, byte structure otherwise untouched. Its value
# is its fidelity: it is the only record of what the registry actually returns, tag soup, stray
# `</font>` end tags, `</br>` closers, CRLF and all.
#
# The root `.gitattributes` says `*.html text eol=lf`, which silently rewrote this capture's line
# endings on commit (the wire response is CRLF). `-text` opts it out of all normalisation so the
# committed blob is the bytes that came off the wire, on every platform.
live_spq_certidao.html -text

